unittitle_ssm: Ari and Helene Bousbib collection of photographs
abstract_ssm: This collection consists of a wide variety of entertainment-themed publicity and on-set photography, portraiture, and photojournalism spanning the period from 1879-1996. Subjects depicted include Broadway theatrical productions, Hollywood film actors, artists, authors, aviators, newscasters, politicians, and other pop culture figures. Also depicted are New York sports, political activism, the 1939 World's Fair, World War II, and other events.
